            <div class="hero-author">Written by <strong>Deva Harsha V</strong></div>
            <p class="hero-hook">
                Some calls aren't meant to be missed. When a broken, un-selected option forces Sushanth into an isolated engineering campus, he uncovers a malicious frequency residing within the dead zones of network architecture—born from an unanswered cry for help.
            </p>
            <a href="#story" class="hero-cta">Enter the Signal</a>
        </div>
        
        <div class="hero-visual">
            <div class="book-cover-container">
